Name: Name Change, Walter Jonas Judah Street, Manhattan

Be it enacted by the Council as follows:

Section 1. The following street name is hereby designated as hereafter indicated.

New namePresent nameLimitsWalter Jonas Judah StreetSt. James Placebetween James Street and Oliver Street
